u+++ date = &ldquo;2017-03-14T18:47:34+01:00&rdquo; title = &ldquo;I have a confession to make&rdquo;
+++
I sincerely believed that my vision of &lsquo;new ways of working&rsquo; was all about the impact of IT, enabling new office concepts to increase productivity with less office space. But now I see that it evolves into the implementation of artificial intelligence, providing new ways to work with fewer people. To paraphrase the title of the book by my colleague Erik Veldhoen, &lsquo;The demise of the office’, I fear for &lsquo;The demise of the employee&rsquo;.
